{"id":12295,"date":"2013-02-18T16:49:04","date_gmt":"2013-02-18T21:49:04","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=12295"},"modified":"2019-05-17T18:02:55","modified_gmt":"2019-05-17T14:02:55","slug":"suicide-funeral-prayer-janazah","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/18\/suicide-funeral-prayer-janazah\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Suicide: Praying over a Muslim who kills himself"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Jabir ibn Samurah reported: A man killed himself and the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, did not pray over him.<\/p>\n<p>Al-Tirmidhi said, \u201cThe people of knowledge disagreed on this issue. Some of them said that the Muslims should perform funeral prayers over every person who prayed towards Mecca, including the one who killed himself. This is the opinion of Sufyan al-Thawri and Ishaq. Ahmad said that the Muslim leader does not perform funeral prayers the one who killed himself, but he is prayed over by others besides him.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1068<\/p>\n<p>Grade:\u00a0<b><i>Sahih\u00a0<\/i><\/b>(authentic) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0645\u064f\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064b\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u062a\u064e\u0644\u064e \u0646\u064e\u0641\u0652\u0633\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0641\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0645\u0652 \u064a\u064f\u0635\u064e\u0644\u0650\u0651 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0631\u0645\u0630\u064a \u0648\u064e\u0627\u062e\u0652\u06