n":0},"title":"Hadith on Jama&#8217;ah: Pray with congregation, even if already prayed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Yazid ibn Al-Aswad reported: I witness the Hajj pilgrimage with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and I prayed the dawn prayer with him in the mosque of Al-Khaif. When the Prophet finished his prayer and turned around, he saw two men in the back of the people\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25538,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/04\/many-salat-one-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":12295,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Performing multiple prayers with single ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 4, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Buraydah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, prayed multiple prayers on the day of liberation with a single ablution and he wiped over his leather socks. Umar said to him, \u201cYou have done something today you have not used to do.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cI have done\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14065,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/08\/killed-defending-property-shahid\/","url_meta":{"origin":12295,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Shahid: Killed defending his wealth is a martyr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is killed defending his property is a martyr.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2480, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 141 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim Imam Ahmad commented, \"Indeed, one may only defend\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31757,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/no-salat-asr-fajr-exceptions\/","url_meta":{"origin":12295,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: No voluntary prayer after \u2018Asr and Fajr, with exceptions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, only prayed two cycles after the afternoon prayer because some property came to him, which occupied him from performing two cycles after the noon prayer. The Prophet prayed them after the afternoon prayer and he did not repeat it.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28905,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/09\/taraweeh-ramadan-imam-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":12295,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Tarawih: Reward for praying with the Imam until he finishes","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, whoever stands for prayer in Ramadan with the Imam until he is finished, it will be recorded as if he prayed the entire night.\u201d Imam al-Tirmidhi commented, \u201cThe scholars differed over the night prayer in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14752,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/28\/salat-no-voluntary-obligatory\/","url_meta":{"origin":12295,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: No voluntary prayer when obligatory prayer begins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen the prayer commences, there is no prayer but the prescribed prayer.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 710 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim Al-Tirmidhi said, \"This was acted upon by some of the people of knowledge among the companions\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/12295","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"r